data.description: Don't miss out on this oppertunity twice. The owners have made a lot of repairs and touchups since the origional photos were posted. This beautiful home in the highly sought after Cedar Lake Estates subdivision is back on the market. Located just minutes away from the amenities The Legends Shoping Center has to offer including Hollywood Casino, Kansas Speedway, the KC Monarchs, and Sporting KC. This beautiful 4 Bed/ 3 bath house is large enough to host the most luxurious gatherings for you and your family or you can step out onto the large covered/screened patio off the back of the house to enjoy bug-free evenings with your friends and family. Cedar Lake Estates is known for hosting several social events throughout the year and is the host of one of the biggest 4th of July fireworks displays in the area which you can enjoy from your front yard or you can take a short walk down the hill to the club house for an upfront view of the festivities. The clubhouse is available to reserve year round for your larger family gatherings complete with a kitchen and multiple bathrooms for your guests. Cedar Lake is stocked with fish by the HOA and is available for fishing at the dock, on the Lake dam or you can take your non-cumbustion engine watercraft onto the lake via the boat ramp.
